{"tid":1673362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［法律問題］點解到而家都未有律師申請臨時禁制令限制水炮車","createTime":"2019-10-24T15:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T17:01:58.000Z","uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d72970e18cf3996cf7bda2ddafcc53d31d24b20","tid":1673362,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:20:48.000Z","msg":"警方在近期處理反修例活動中出動水炮車及噴射顏色水。綠色和平今晚（24日）在facebook表示，早前取得「顏色水」樣本，並送到實驗室化驗，初步結果顯示「顏色水」含有色素以及黏合劑；綜合文獻及市民接觸後的反應，「推測『顏色水』有機會含有有害嘅催淚溶液」。本報正向警方查詢「顏色水」成分，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平在facebook指出，雖然目前仍未能完全分析出「顏色水」所有成分，以及確認是否含有其他有害或具毒性化合物，但綜合立法會文件《Legislative Council Panel on Security Specialised Crowd Management Vehicles》、國際文獻《Handbook of Toxicology of Chemical Warfare Agents》、專家意見，以及市民接觸後的身體反應，推測「顏色水」有可能含有有害的催淚溶液（包含Pelargonic Acid Vanillylamide Solution），或另外兩種催淚性有毒化合物CN（Chloroacetophenone）和CS（2-Chlorobenzylidene malononitrile），相信並非只有色素。<br />\n<br />\n綠色和平表示，雖然「顏色水」所含的化合物致命風險較低，但可能對人體構成嚴重的即時不適反應，其中催淚溶液（Pelargonic Acid Vanillylamide Solution）對人體的反應，與胡椒噴霧（辣椒油樹脂Oleoresin capsicum）類近。組織引述《香港醫學雜誌》就胡椒噴霧的臨牀影響文獻研究，該化合物對眼睛及呼吸系統均有直接影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/greenpeacehk/photos/a.311164940500/10162342657465501/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgreenpeacehk%2Fphotos%2Fa.311164940500%2F10162342657465501%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=569bd046\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/greenpeacehk/photos/a.311164940500/10162342657465501/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左水炮車，仲有冇得申請限制克警帶實彈上現場？<br />\n<br />\n直至司法覆核？<br />\n<br />\n真心唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b6733c05cd1dc9ea8ae7b66b2bca4f791f7424","tid":1673362,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbYpESe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbYpESe.jpg&h=6c0e53db&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fbbc8c52e532b567d917293dcdf57b6d4f0426d5","tid":1673362,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:21:55.000Z","msg":"推到有律師上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce39bf974b9567fae0f48ae8d8e60f917f1b67d","tid":1673362,"uid":253809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"so terrible...."},{"pid":"0cb325a4a68e47f9eff194502dd3baf364904fe2","tid":1673362,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:28:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b8f80f5abf739847811a263b1ff59741f8959316","tid":1673362,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"班官咪又係同班狗一夥"},{"pid":"697670dc7cfb11de4e8263cf0ad12187fae1ce08","tid":1673362,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f80f5abf739847811a263b1ff59741f8959316","tid":1673362,"uid":91321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:31:19.000Z","msg":"班官咪又係同班狗一夥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"唔放棄每一個機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b92c5e50df8fa49a570af1e8a854a285351b2fc","tid":1673362,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"211ee29326566829705cfc861da76ec899826bef","tid":1673362,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"64b9dfd92f2d7667a4835fca6c8ed96bd237668b","tid":1673362,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}